The '''Orange''' is a [[Fruits|fruit]] grown by planting an [[Orange Sapling]], waiting 28 days for it to grow into an [[Orange Tree]], and harvesting the tree during the [[Summer]].

An Orange may be purchased at the [[Traveling Cart]] for {{tprice|100}} or found in [[The Cave]] on the farm, if the fruit bat option is chosen.
==Gifting==
